Hellooooooooo Everyoooooooone!!

I've got a new story to share with you all today! I hope you enjoy it! Winds of Change is a story about a depressed guy named Will who is in his mid-30s and realizing he hasn't been living his life the he wanted. After his best friend and scientist, Mark, offers him a deal of the lifetime his life begins to become much more interesting!

UPDATE 11/1/25-
I updated all of the images in this gallery to add the little speech bubble tails to make it easier to read the story. I hope you enjoy it and it's easier to read!!
